Mailing List Commands:

@{b}Subscribe@{ub}
    Adds the senders E-Mail address to the list. If you are already subscribed
    then Rhyme will ignore this command and pass the mail onto the rest of the
    list

@{b}Remove@{ub}
    Removes the sender from the list. @{b}MUST@{ub} be the only word in the
    subject

@{b}ListUsers@{ub}
    Replies with the list of people on the list

@{b}Help@{ub}
    Sends the current Help File for the list. @{b}MUST@{ub} be the only word in
    the subject.


